Chapter 1\.md            8      http://api\.getcloudapp\.com/\.\.\.
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0
.
.P
List newest, deleted drops:
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf

$ cloudapp list \-\-filter=trash
Name       Views  Href
Delete Me  0      http://api\.getcloudapp\.com/\.\.\.
  \.\.\.
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0
.
.P
